The undersigned is directed to inform all Members of
the Council of Ministers that the Prime Minister has decided
that the Minister of Rehabilitation should also be in charge
of work relating to Minority Affairs. Henceforth, his
designation will be "Minister of Rehabilitation and Minority
Affairs".
